<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>@ViewData["Title"] - 設備維修管理系統</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/lib/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/site.css" asp-append-version="true" />
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-sm navbar-toggleable-sm navbar-light bg-white border-bottom box-shadow mb-3">
            <div class="container-fluid">
                <a class="navbar-brand" asp-area="" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index">設備維修管理系統</a>
                <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collaㄐpse" data-bs-target=".navbar-collapse" aria-controls="navbarSupportedContent"
                        aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                    <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
                </button>
                <div class="navbar-collapse collapse d-sm-inline-flex justify-content-between">
                    <ul class="navbar-nav flex-grow-1">
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link text-dark" asp-area="" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index">首頁</a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link text-dark" asp-area="" asp-controller="Customers" asp-action="Index">客戶管理</a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link text-dark" asp-area="" asp-controller="Devices" asp-action="Index">設備管理</a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link text-dark" asp-area="" asp-controller="Employees" asp-action="Index">員工管理</a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link text-dark" asp-area="" asp-controller="RepairCases" asp-action="Index">維修案件</a>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </header>
    <div class="container">
        <main role="main" class="pb-3">
            @RenderBody()
        </main>
    </div>

    <footer class="border-top footer text-muted">
        <div class="container">
            &copy; 2025 - 設備維修管理系統
        </div>
    </footer>

    @* 【關鍵 1】載入 jQuery 和 Bootstrap 的核心腳本 *@
    @* 這兩個是許多互動功能（包括我們自己的腳本）的基礎 *@
    <script src="~/lib/jquery/dist/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="~/lib/bootstrap/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script src="~/js/site.js" asp-append-version="true"></script>

    @* 【關鍵 2】這是解決問題的魔法！ *@
    @* 這行程式碼的作用是：如果在某個子頁面 (例如 Create.cshtml) 中定義了名為 "Scripts" 的 section， *@
    @* 就把那個 section 裡的內容（也就是我們寫的 jQuery 連動選單程式碼）渲染到這裡。 *@
    @* 如果沒有這一行，我們在 Create.cshtml 寫的所有 JavaScript 都會被忽略。 *@
    @await RenderSectionAsync("Scripts", required: false)
</body>
</html>